window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Kaiden Jericho's life just went sideways.</b></p> <p>He has been working odd jobs since the first school year ended.</p> <p><i>(People have to eat, right?)</i></p> <p>The problem? He isn't as prepared as he thinks he is.</p> <p>Out in the jungles of the Amazon, Kaiden meets a new set of nightmares, and death there is permanent.</p> <p><b>Even with all his previous training in the Animus, will Kaiden survive?</b></p> <p>You don't become the best of the best by staying alive. In the Animus, you are closer to perfection with each death you suffer.</p> <p>Kaiden Jericho would rather skip the death part, thank you very much.</p> <p><i>Includes special note from co-author Michael Anderle.</i></p>"; 
